stories.text: They'll release something only to kill it a few months later. Is anyone taking Google IO seriously?
stories.title: Does anyone care anymore what Google demos in IO?

stories.text:
I am interested in moving inland from Palo Alto closer toward Yosemite. I just want to be able to drive to Palo Alto within 2 to 3 hours once or twice a month for special occasions, but otherwise enjoy cheaper rent.

I am familiar with cities along the coast, but not the ones post San Francisco Premium Outlet. Has anyone moved in this direction? Any cities you would recommend?
